T1  - Liquidity commonality and return co-movement
AU  - Domowitz, Ian
AU  - Hansch, Oliver
AU  - Wang, Xiaoxin
JO  - Journal of Financial Markets
VL  - 8
IS  - 4
SP  - 351
EP  - 376
PY  - 2005
